summary:
I am a young, hardworking and aspiring Mathematician. I graduated with a BScHons Mathematics, with a research project based in Functional Analysis with the Title "Geometrical Constants of Banach Spaces" in the year following my BSc Mathematics at the University of Pretoria. I am currently doing my MSc in Mathematics at Leiden University with interest in specialising in Algebraic Number Theory and/or p-Adic Functional Analysis, with graduation expected around June 2024.
I'm an avid problem solver, and enjoy learning more than anything.
